  "description": "The image depicts a rocky beach or riverbed with large, weathered boulders and pebbles scattered across a dark, granular surface. A prominent pinkish-grey boulder dominates the foreground, its rough texture contrasting with the smoother stones around it. Behind this, a steep embankment rises, composed of layers of grey and beige rock, partially covered with sparse green vegetation. The sky is a clear, bright blue, suggesting a sunny day. The scene conveys a sense of natural, geological forces and the passage of time.",
